    <stitle>SINGLE REDUCTION, TANDEM DRIVE AXLES: EATON - DESCRIPTION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="5">
        <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
        <para>Instructions contained herein cover three basic axle models. Their design is common, with differences in
            load capacity. Capacity variations are achieved by combining basic differential carrier assemblies with
            different axle housings, axle shafts, and wheel equipment.
        </para>
