        <para>Suffix letter "P" indicates lube pump is standard (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1401304">Figure 4</hotlnk>). (P) indicates axle is available with or without lube pump.
            Pump models are equipped with a gerotor pump and filter, designed to provide additional lubrication to the
            inter-axle differential and related parts.
        </para>
